description: These are the photon ID Scale Factors (nominal, up or down) for 2022FG Prompt Reco dataset. They are available for the cut-based and MVA IDs. They are dependent on the transverse momenta and pseudorapidity of the photon. Please keep in the mind that if your analysis is sensitive to high pT photons (>500 GeV), we recommend you to use HEEP ID. In any case, you have even some photons above 500 GeV, be careful while applying these SFs.

inputs.description: sf/sfup/sfdown (sfup = sf + syst, sfdown = sf - syst)
